summary: I feel like running away and starting my life somewhere else. Im tired of my house and of the people ive met there. Its like my...
body: I feel like running away and starting my life somewhere else. Im tired of my house and of the people ive met there. Its like my creativity is getting so stuck by being around the same people all the time and talking about only the same aubjects as always. I need new air. I need new people. I wanna met new artists. I wamma get to know about their process. I wanna read the books they are reading and watch the movies they are watching and look through their sketchbooks and feel their work around me. Idk. I feel stuck into myself. I wanna live as other people.

summary: okay here’s some oc art after all those times i said I didn’t want to draw any.[[MORE]] His name is Chili, yes, like the...
caption:
okay here’s some oc art after all those times i said I didn’t want to draw any.

His name is Chili, yes, like the vegetable. Out in public, he’s outgoing and super extroverted, but alone and in his own time, he’s rather quiet and actually shy. His image of the “cool guy” gets harder to keep up as time goes by lmao. At this point, he’s trying to be the college waste away while being the stressed college waste away at the same time. Of course, that’s only expected since he’s striving to become a doctor.
